title: Nordo in for PA! Micheletti, Gleeman, Lo Duca join!
description:
Meatsauce, Cory Cove, and Nordo square off in the name game.
Pat Micheletti talks all things Stanley Cup Final and MN Wild Latest with Nordo...
Aaron Gleeman hops in studio to break down the latest from around the world of the Twins and NBA talk as well.
Plus, former MLB catcher and current horse-racing expert Paul Lo Duca previews leg three of the Triple Crown as we handicap Justify's chances at taking home the trophy.
